{"id":8145,"date":"2024-01-22T02:33:52","date_gmt":"2020-04-21T21:03:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=8145"},"modified":"2023-07-26T12:18:24","modified_gmt":"2023-07-26T06:48:24","slug":"closet-organization-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/closet-organization-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Closet Organization Ideas To Maximise Your Storage Space"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>From messy Mondays to Thank God It&#8217;s Friday, don&#8217;t let your closet follow your mood swings. Explore these ideas to keep your closet neat and tidy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>\u201cOut of clutter, find simplicity. From discord, find harmony. In the middle of difficulty lies opportunity.\u201d &#8211; Albert Einstein<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you reminded of discord and disharmony everytime you open your closet? Have you ever had one of those weekday mornings when you open your closet to get ready and out comes an avalanche of clothes? Closets are often the messiest and least organised parts of our homes. They receive no attention as they are often out of sight.&nbsp; However, you can make your wardrobe an epitome of style, luxury and order. A neat closet will let you dump things in a hurry or store a dead body (just kidding). In this blog we will look at a few ideas that will help you organise your closet to maximise your storage space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Invest In A Clothing Rack With Hanger Rods<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It is<strong> <\/strong>always a good idea to have rods to hang your clothes instead of piling them up in a messy mound. Organising your clothes this way not only saves time digging through a large pile, but also gives you loads of space to stack in more clothes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020338\/closet-organizer-ideas-for-your-home-with-a-clothing-rack-and-hanger-rods.jpg\" alt=\"Closet organizer for your home with a clothing rack and hanger rods with a loads of space for clothes\" class=\"wp-image-8219\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020338\/closet-organizer-ideas-for-your-home-with-a-clothing-rack-and-hanger-rods.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020338\/closet-organizer-ideas-for-your-home-with-a-clothing-rack-and-hanger-rods-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020338\/closet-organizer-ideas-for-your-home-with-a-clothing-rack-and-hanger-rods-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020338\/closet-organizer-ideas-for-your-home-with-a-clothing-rack-and-hanger-rods-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020502\/closet-organizer-ideas-for-your-home-with-a-clothing-rack-and-hanger-rods-1.jpg\" alt=\"Closet organizer ideas for your home with with a clothing rack and hanger rods\" class=\"wp-image-8220\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020502\/closet-organizer-ideas-for-your-home-with-a-clothing-rack-and-hanger-rods-1.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020502\/closet-organizer-ideas-for-your-home-with-a-clothing-rack-and-hanger-rods-1-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020502\/closet-organizer-ideas-for-your-home-with-a-clothing-rack-and-hanger-rods-1-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020502\/closet-organizer-ideas-for-your-home-with-a-clothing-rack-and-hanger-rods-1-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Looking for modern closet designs for your master bedroom\" src=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/looking-for-modern-closet-designs-for-your-master-bedroom.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Organize With Shelves, Drawers And Wicker Baskets<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>An easy way to turn chaos into order is by using shelves to store bulky bed linen that is used daily like blankets, covers and bedsheets. They do not require gentle handling or ironing and are best tucked away on open shelves. Drawers can also be used to store accessories, cosmetics, or other smaller items. Wicker baskets are the best way to put your old or dirty laundry in a pile without it being an eyesore. Place them in the bottom most shelf to quickly put away all your soiled clothes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020629\/closet-organisation-for-your-home-with-shelves-drawers-and-wicker-baskets.jpg\" alt=\"Closet organisation for our home where you can organise with shelves, drawers and wicker baskets\" class=\"wp-image-8221\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020629\/closet-organisation-for-your-home-with-shelves-drawers-and-wicker-baskets.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020629\/closet-organisation-for-your-home-with-shelves-drawers-and-wicker-baskets-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020629\/closet-organisation-for-your-home-with-shelves-drawers-and-wicker-baskets-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020629\/closet-organisation-for-your-home-with-shelves-drawers-and-wicker-baskets-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020820\/best-closet-organizer-system-with-shelves-and-drawers.jpg\" alt=\"Best closet organiser system for your home where you can organise shelves and baskets easily\" class=\"wp-image-8222\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020820\/best-closet-organizer-system-with-shelves-and-drawers.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020820\/best-closet-organizer-system-with-shelves-and-drawers-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020820\/best-closet-organizer-system-with-shelves-and-drawers-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020820\/best-closet-organizer-system-with-shelves-and-drawers-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-wall-shelves\/\">Living Room Wall Shelves Designs For Your Home<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Doors! There\u2019s More To Them Than What Meets The Eye<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When low on space the backs of doors can literally open up endless storage possibilities. From hooks and hangers to narrow shelves or even open boxes, you can customise the back of your closet doors to maximise your storage potential by freeing up space inside the closet.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020937\/closet-organisation-ideas-with-hooks-and-hangers.jpg\" alt=\"Closet organisation ideas with hooks and hangers to narrow shelves or even open boxes\" class=\"wp-image-8223\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020937\/closet-organisation-ideas-with-hooks-and-hangers.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020937\/closet-organisation-ideas-with-hooks-and-hangers-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020937\/closet-organisation-ideas-with-hooks-and-hangers-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22020937\/closet-organisation-ideas-with-hooks-and-hangers-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Design A Closet With A Sliding Door<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you tired of walking from one end to the other looking for your clothes and accessories? Well then, it&#8217;s time you consider a sliding door wardrobe. Sliding doors closets are great space savers and work well in tight corners where two doors will swing into each other. You can design a wardrobe with deeper storage thanks to sliding doors.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021116\/closet-organisation-tips-small-closets-with-a-sliding-door.jpg\" alt=\"Closet organisation tips small closets with a sliding door for clothes and accessories which are great space savers\" class=\"wp-image-8224\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021116\/closet-organisation-tips-small-closets-with-a-sliding-door.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021116\/closet-organisation-tips-small-closets-with-a-sliding-door-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021116\/closet-organisation-tips-small-closets-with-a-sliding-door-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021116\/closet-organisation-tips-small-closets-with-a-sliding-door-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-bedroom-cupboard-designs\/\">Modern Cupboard Designs For Your Bedroom<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Say No To Ironing, Use A Trouser Organiser <\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p> Nobody likes to iron! Get away from having to iron your trousers every morning with a dedicated pant organiser that will keep your trousers neat and wrinkle free. Most pants or trousers require minimal to no ironing if they are folded up right after washing. These organisers will help you do just that by making that process as easy as it can be. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021353\/closet-organization-ideas-with-a-trouser-organiser.jpg\" alt=\"Closet organisation ideas with a trouser organiser which keep your trousers neat and wrinkle free\" class=\"wp-image-8225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021353\/closet-organization-ideas-with-a-trouser-organiser.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021353\/closet-organization-ideas-with-a-trouser-organiser-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021353\/closet-organization-ideas-with-a-trouser-organiser-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021353\/closet-organization-ideas-with-a-trouser-organiser-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mirror, Mirror On The Wall!&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A mirror inside your closet or on the back of a closet door is a good design feature as it helps you quickly get ready without having to run to the bathroom or dressing area. Now you can quickly try on hats, ties, belts, handbags right in front of your closet and save time when you&#8217;re late for that party.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021501\/bedroom-closet-small-closet-organization-ideas-with-mirror.jpg\" alt=\"bedroom closet small closet organisation ideas with mirror on the back of the closet door\" class=\"wp-image-8226\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021501\/bedroom-closet-small-closet-organization-ideas-with-mirror.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021501\/bedroom-closet-small-closet-organization-ideas-with-mirror-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021501\/bedroom-closet-small-closet-organization-ideas-with-mirror-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021501\/bedroom-closet-small-closet-organization-ideas-with-mirror-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An Island To The Rescue<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Get rid of the &#8216;chair&#8217; that houses an avalanche of clothes. Instead build yourself an island. Assuming you have ample space in your closet room or own a walk-in wardrobe you can benefit with an island. It will help you maximise storage space for all your accessories such as belts and bags. It can also act as a dresser if you place a vanity mirror on top. An island also gives you extra surface area to sort of clothes. Not to mention it becomes the major focal point for the room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021620\/entry-closet-organisation-ideas-with-a-walk-in-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Entry closet organisation ideas with as island or a walk-in wardrobe where you can  maximise storage space \" class=\"wp-image-8227\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021620\/entry-closet-organisation-ideas-with-a-walk-in-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021620\/entry-closet-organisation-ideas-with-a-walk-in-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021620\/entry-closet-organisation-ideas-with-a-walk-in-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22021620\/entry-closet-organisation-ideas-with-a-walk-in-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Design Cafe\u2019s Design Tips<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><strong>Label<\/strong>: Though this sounds like more work &#8211; labeling drawers, boxes, compartments &#8211; for designated items will enforce the habit of putting away things where they belong. This will make your job of searching for everything easier in the future.<\/li><li><strong>Donate:<\/strong> Give away all your old clothes and accessories you no longer use. If you want to share some of your ideas<\/li><li><strong>Buy appropriately:<\/strong> Do not buy unnecessary things only to repent later. Your closet only needs essentials &#8211; not a dress when you wore on your first date!<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22023317\/bedroom-closet-organization-ideas-where-you-can-label-items-1.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom closet organisation ideas where you can label items such as drawers, boxes, compartments\" class=\"wp-image-8233\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22023317\/bedroom-closet-organization-ideas-where-you-can-label-items-1.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22023317\/bedroom-closet-organization-ideas-where-you-can-label-items-1-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22023317\/bedroom-closet-organization-ideas-where-you-can-label-items-1-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/22023317\/bedroom-closet-organization-ideas-where-you-can-label-items-1-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/home-organisation-ideas\/\">Great Home Organisation Tips And Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield f